WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:05.000
Funtime Kids

00:05.000 --> 00:07.000
The best use of time

00:07.000 --> 00:10.000
The person who makes the best use of time

00:10.000 --> 00:14.000
gets good results with time

00:14.000 --> 00:17.000
This is what happened when Sonu and Vani's

00:17.000 --> 00:19.000
annual exams were about to come

00:19.000 --> 00:21.000
Hey, are you still studying?

00:21.000 --> 00:23.000
Come, let's eat

00:23.000 --> 00:25.000
Only a small project is left

00:25.000 --> 00:28.000
If we don't do it, the teacher will scold us

00:28.000 --> 00:31.000
And the exams are starting from next week

00:31.000 --> 00:33.000
Vani was a very hardworking

00:33.000 --> 00:36.000
and a good use of time kid

00:36.000 --> 00:38.000
Whereas her brother Sonu

00:38.000 --> 00:41.000
was a very careless and naughty kid

00:41.000 --> 00:43.000
He used to postpone everything

00:43.000 --> 00:45.000
Is your project done?

00:45.000 --> 00:47.000
Yes, the project has to be done

00:47.000 --> 00:49.000
in the 6th period

00:49.000 --> 00:52.000
There are still 2 periods left

00:52.000 --> 00:54.000
I will do it quickly

00:54.000 --> 00:56.000
Now come fast, I am hungry

00:56.000 --> 00:58.000
And I have to play too

00:58.000 --> 01:00.000
Hey Sonu, wait

01:00.000 --> 01:02.000
If you don't do it, the teacher will scold you

01:02.000 --> 01:04.000
Sonu and Vani's parents

01:04.000 --> 01:06.000
always used to give Sonu

01:06.000 --> 01:08.000
an example of Vani and make him understand

01:08.000 --> 01:11.000
Look Sonu, you have grown up now

01:11.000 --> 01:13.000
Along with playing, you should

01:13.000 --> 01:15.000
also concentrate on your studies

01:15.000 --> 01:17.000
Yes mummy, from tomorrow for sure

01:17.000 --> 01:20.000
Sonu, learn to make good use of time

01:20.000 --> 01:22.000
from your sister

01:22.000 --> 01:24.000
Look, she studies with time

01:24.000 --> 01:26.000
She plays with time

01:26.000 --> 01:28.000
She never postpones today's work

01:28.000 --> 01:30.000
for tomorrow

01:30.000 --> 01:32.000
You see, from tomorrow

01:32.000 --> 01:34.000
I will also do the same

01:34.000 --> 01:36.000
Shall I go and play now?

01:36.000 --> 01:38.000
Please!

01:38.000 --> 01:40.000
Sonu's carelessness was increasing

01:40.000 --> 01:42.000
day by day

01:42.000 --> 01:44.000
And finally

01:44.000 --> 01:46.000
the days of the exams

01:46.000 --> 01:48.000
were nearing

01:48.000 --> 01:50.000
Only 2 days were left

01:50.000 --> 01:52.000
for Sonu and Vani's exams

01:52.000 --> 01:54.000
Listen, from next Monday

01:54.000 --> 01:56.000
your exams are starting

01:56.000 --> 01:58.000
right?

01:58.000 --> 02:00.000
Study hard

02:00.000 --> 02:02.000
and do well in the exams

02:02.000 --> 02:04.000
Sonu, I am

02:04.000 --> 02:06.000
really worried about you

02:06.000 --> 02:08.000
You always postpone

02:08.000 --> 02:10.000
today's work for tomorrow

02:10.000 --> 02:12.000
Don't postpone your studies for tomorrow

02:12.000 --> 02:14.000
Like Vani,

02:14.000 --> 02:16.000
study all the lessons on time

02:16.000 --> 02:18.000
Okay?

02:18.000 --> 02:20.000
Papa, there are still 2 days

02:20.000 --> 02:22.000
left for the exams

02:22.000 --> 02:24.000
I will study everything

02:24.000 --> 02:26.000
I am going to play now

02:26.000 --> 02:28.000
Till I don't play

02:28.000 --> 02:30.000
I won't be able to study

02:38.000 --> 02:40.000
Vani, look

02:40.000 --> 02:42.000
what a beautiful weather

02:42.000 --> 02:44.000
Come, let's play

02:44.000 --> 02:46.000
for a while

02:46.000 --> 02:48.000
We can study later

02:48.000 --> 02:50.000
Everything will be done soon

02:50.000 --> 02:52.000
Yes, the weather is beautiful

02:52.000 --> 02:54.000
But I have to

02:54.000 --> 02:56.000
complete my lessons

02:56.000 --> 02:58.000
Tomorrow is the exams

02:58.000 --> 03:00.000
Playing in this weather

03:00.000 --> 03:02.000
is something else

03:02.000 --> 03:04.000
You keep studying

03:04.000 --> 03:06.000
I am going to play

03:06.000 --> 03:08.000
After a while, Vani saw

03:08.000 --> 03:10.000
that the beautiful weather

03:10.000 --> 03:12.000
is slowly taking the form of a storm

03:12.000 --> 03:14.000
And the dark clouds

03:14.000 --> 03:16.000
are swirling

03:16.000 --> 03:18.000
This can happen anytime

03:18.000 --> 03:20.000
Seeing the weather

03:20.000 --> 03:22.000
Vani was worried

03:22.000 --> 03:24.000
that if it rains

03:24.000 --> 03:26.000
how will she complete her lessons

03:26.000 --> 03:28.000
Because in the rains

03:28.000 --> 03:30.000
the electricity of the house

03:30.000 --> 03:32.000
is cut off

03:32.000 --> 03:34.000
She called out to Sonu

03:34.000 --> 03:36.000
Sonu, listen

03:36.000 --> 03:38.000
It looks like it's going to rain

03:38.000 --> 03:40.000
Maybe the electricity will be cut off at night

03:40.000 --> 03:42.000
Stop playing and

03:42.000 --> 03:44.000
come and complete your lessons

03:44.000 --> 03:46.000
What will you write to me?

03:46.000 --> 03:48.000
Don't worry, Vani

03:48.000 --> 03:50.000
It's afternoon now

03:50.000 --> 03:52.000
I will finish everything

03:52.000 --> 03:54.000
at night

03:54.000 --> 03:56.000
The electricity won't be cut off

03:56.000 --> 03:58.000
It will be fun to study

03:58.000 --> 04:00.000
after the rain

04:00.000 --> 04:02.000
I am going now

04:02.000 --> 04:04.000
Sonu played till late evening

04:04.000 --> 04:06.000
But she was worried

04:06.000 --> 04:08.000
when the rain started

04:08.000 --> 04:10.000
Sonu got scared

04:10.000 --> 04:12.000
and returned home

04:12.000 --> 04:14.000
She saw that

04:14.000 --> 04:16.000
there was no electricity

04:16.000 --> 04:18.000
in the entire village

04:18.000 --> 04:20.000
Seeing this

04:20.000 --> 04:22.000
Sonu started crying

04:24.000 --> 04:26.000
What will happen to me

04:26.000 --> 04:28.000
in the exam tomorrow?

04:28.000 --> 04:30.000
I didn't study a single lesson

04:30.000 --> 04:32.000
And now there is no electricity

04:32.000 --> 04:34.000
I will fail

04:36.000 --> 04:38.000
I told you

04:38.000 --> 04:40.000
to study your lessons

04:40.000 --> 04:42.000
on time

04:42.000 --> 04:44.000
I told you a week ago

04:44.000 --> 04:46.000
to study on time

04:46.000 --> 04:48.000
But you never understood

04:48.000 --> 04:50.000
Now suffer

04:50.000 --> 04:52.000
Sorry, Papa

04:52.000 --> 04:54.000
What do I do now?

04:54.000 --> 04:56.000
I wish

04:56.000 --> 04:58.000
I had studied my lessons

04:58.000 --> 05:00.000
on time

05:02.000 --> 05:04.000
She understood

05:04.000 --> 05:06.000
that because of her carelessness

05:06.000 --> 05:08.000
she didn't have time to study

05:08.000 --> 05:10.000
Crying won't help

05:10.000 --> 05:12.000
Now do you understand

05:12.000 --> 05:14.000
why everyone used to explain you?

05:14.000 --> 05:16.000
Now stop crying

05:16.000 --> 05:18.000
and come with me

05:18.000 --> 05:20.000
I had completed my studies

05:20.000 --> 05:22.000
on time

05:22.000 --> 05:24.000
I will teach you all the lessons

05:24.000 --> 05:26.000
and remind you

05:26.000 --> 05:28.000
The next day

05:28.000 --> 05:30.000
both the children went to the exam

05:30.000 --> 05:32.000
The one who respects time

05:32.000 --> 05:34.000
in the future

05:34.000 --> 05:38.000
is great!

